visual_elements.description: A plan view diagram illustrating the dimensions for a carport parking space. It shows a car parked within a rectangular space. Dimensions indicate 'open' space on one side and '20' min. open' for the length. It also points to 'One of 2 corner columns' and 'Driveway/parking surface'.

A left side elevation diagram illustrating the dimensions for a covered parking space (carport). It shows a car parked under a sloped roof supported by columns. Dimensions indicate '20' min. open' for the width and '7' min. open' for the height. Labels point to 'One of 2 corner columns' and 'Bottom roof system'.

A front elevation diagram illustrating the dimensions for a covered parking space (carport). It shows a car parked under a sloped roof supported by columns. Dimensions indicate '10' min open' for the width and '7' min. open' for the height. Labels point to 'One of 2 corner columns' and 'Bottom roof system'.
